reviewText: I thought I was going to get the whole dvd , I was wrong,  there are three parts, I only got  one part of dvd

This is a total rip-off! I bought this thinking that it was something that I haven't seen before. Instead, it's an overpriced episode of the History Channel Gangland covering the Vice Lords. I paid over $20 for a burnt copy of one episode of Gangland. I want a refund!!
